<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219622>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 12. Adults of Eulamprotes spp. 1, E. wilkella (Zeller), ♂ (Italy); 2, ditto, ♂ (Great Britain, England); 3, ditto, ♀ (Italy); 4, E. ochricapilla (Rebel), ♂ (Italy); 5, ditto, ♀ (Austria); 6, E. superbella (Zeller), ♂ (Austria); 7, ditto, ♂ (Italy); 8, ditto, ♀ (Denmark); 9, E. mirusella sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (France); 10, ditto, paratype, ♀ (France); 11, E. baldizzonei sp. nov., paratype, ♂ (Italy); 12, ditto, paratype, ♂ (Italy). Scale bar = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219622/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219624>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22 – 27. Male genitalia of Eulamprotes spp. 22, E. wilkella (Zeller), (Macedonia) gen. slide GEL 1194 P. Huemer; 23, ditto, phallus; 24, E. ochricapilla (Rebel), (Macedonia) gen. slide GEL 1186 P. Huemer; 25, ditto, phallus; 26, E. superbella (Zeller), (Denmark) gen. slide GU 13 / 1342 P. Huemer; 27, ditto, phallus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219624/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219629>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50 – 51. Female genitalia of Eulamprotes spp. 50, E. wilkella (Zeller), (Italy) gen. slide GEL 1229 P. Huemer; 51, E. ochricapilla (Rebel), (Austria) gen. slide GEL 1228 P. Huemer." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219629/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219630>
    dc:description "FIGURES 52 – 53. Female genitalia of Eulamprotes spp. 52, E. superbella (Zeller), (Denmark) gen. slide GU 13 / 1343 P. Huemer; 53, E. mirusella sp. nov., paratype, (France) gen. slide GU 13 / 1362 P. Huemer." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219630/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

